1
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:33,030
Clearing the emperor's side.

2
00:00:33,030 --> 00:00:34,090
Is this Old Demon Gu

3
00:00:34,530 --> 00:00:36,660
really going to send troops to Zhongzhou

4
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:38,330
and attack the ancestral court of the Human race head-on?

5
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:38,860
Crazy.

6
00:00:39,300 --> 00:00:40,430
He's really crazy.

7
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,560
The ancestral court is where the destiny of the Human race lies.

8
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:45,430
The foundations of the major Human Emperor families

9
00:00:45,430 --> 00:00:46,490
are not weak at all.

10
00:00:47,460 --> 00:00:50,900
Does Gu Linyuan really want to sink Zhongzhou?

11
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:00,500
All forces attack!

12
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:14,300
The Human Emperor is immoral,

13
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:16,000
favoring demonic men.

14
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:17,430
Her Majesty favors demonic men.

15
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:18,260
Favoring demonic men.

16
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:18,800
Really?

17
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,160
No wonder there have been

18
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:22,289
so many rumors from the palace lately.

19
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,460
What a 'clearing the emperor's side'!

20
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:26,630
You bold fanatic!

21
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:28,830
I am the Human Emperor ordained by heaven.

22
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:30,300
Recognized by the Human Emperor Cauldron,

23
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:31,400
I am the chosen one.

24
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:35,000
What is Gu Linyuan

25
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:36,630
to dare to clear my side?

26
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:38,100
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

27
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:39,960
The Emperor's Pass is engraved with countless ancient formation patterns,

28
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:40,930
possessing immense power.

29
00:01:40,930 --> 00:01:42,830
The Demons absolutely cannot break through it in a short time.

30
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:43,700
The top priority now

31
00:01:43,700 --> 00:01:44,860
is to purge the Gu family first,

32
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:45,930
lest rumors spread,

33
00:01:45,930 --> 00:01:46,560
unsettle the people,

34
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,160
and affect the orthodox status of our ancestral court.

35
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,430
If I don't make an example of them,

36
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:50,630
how can I establish my prestige

37
00:01:50,630 --> 00:01:52,030
and convince the masses?

38
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:58,560
Where is Jiang Yun?

39
00:01:58,759 --> 00:01:59,490
Get out here!

40
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,130
It's the one Her Majesty issued a suppression order against,

41
00:02:05,130 --> 00:02:06,400
that Sin Clan Quasi-Emperor.

42
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,699
She actually dares to fight her way back to the ancient city of the Human Emperor.

43
00:02:08,699 --> 00:02:10,360
It's all because she neglected her duty

44
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,160
that the Demons invaded in large numbers.

45
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:14,220
She really colluded with the Demons.

46
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:24,100
Luo Jinghong!

47
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,660
As a Human Quasi-Emperor,

48
00:02:25,730 --> 00:02:26,930
you actually neglected your duty,

49
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:27,800
colluded with the Demons,

50
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,329
and allowed the Demon army to invade,

51
00:02:29,329 --> 00:02:31,560
bringing endless disasters to our Xuantian Continent!

52
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:31,800
You

53
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,829
cannot atone for your crimes even with ten thousand deaths!

54
00:02:32,829 --> 00:02:34,700
What a 'cannot atone even with ten thousand deaths'!

55
00:02:34,700 --> 00:02:36,900
I defended the Emperor's Pass for the ancestral court for thousands of years,

56
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:38,430
slaying countless demons.

57
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,030
Yet you slaughtered my clansmen behind my back

58
00:02:40,030 --> 00:02:41,800
and forcefully branded my Luo Clan with the name of Sin Blood.

59
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,960
This grudge is irreconcilable!

60
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,760
Let me ask you,

61
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,560
as for the tens of thousands of my Luo clansmen,

62
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,730
where are they now?

63
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:47,360
How dare you!

64
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,200
Spreading fallacies to deceive the people.

65
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,160
Your intentions are punishable by death!

66
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,430
The Luo Clan colluded with the Demons,

67
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:51,829
attempting to shake the foundation of our Human race.

68
00:02:51,829 --> 00:02:53,430
They have long been demoted to Sin Blood.

69
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:54,829
Human Emperor Cauldron,

70
00:02:55,230 --> 00:02:56,030
suppress them

71
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:56,800
for me!

72
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:33,200
So what if you're at the peak of the quasi-Emperor realm?

73
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,630
In this ancient city of the Human Emperor,

74
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,600
I am blessed with endless luck of the human race

75
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,660
and command the Human Emperor Cauldron.

76
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:38,960
I am absolutely invincible.

77
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,160
I

78
00:03:39,329 --> 00:03:40,700
am the destined Human Emperor.

79
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:42,360
If Gu Linyuan really has the guts

80
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,160
to set foot here,

81
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,000
I am here.

82
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,120
What can you do?

83
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:16,459
Although Gu Linyuan is strong,

84
00:04:16,730 --> 00:04:17,860
what he is facing now

85
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:19,600
is the entire Ancestral Court of the human race

86
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,800
with tens of thousands of years of heritage.

87
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,959
Gu Linyuan is really crazy.

88
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:24,030
Does he want to exhaust the heritage of the Imperial Clan?

89
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:25,460
The strength of the Ancestral Court of the human race

90
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:27,460
can be traced back to ancient times.

91
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,330
I am here.

92
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,830
What can

93
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:32,760
you do?

94
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,930
This aura...

95
00:04:37,730 --> 00:04:38,860
This tone...

96
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:41,260
The mysterious voice

97
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,860
that has been echoing in my mind...
